[Vanilla Void Yacht Club]

'Get on board!

This is VVY(Vanilla Void Yacht) NFT with IRL benefit.

1. Each project itself, collectable NFT art piece, limited editions!
2. IRL benefits 100% include, luxury Yacht experience with premium champagnes!
3. Future benefits as early Vanilla Void crews! such as white list, early information sharing, limited merchant, and so on!

[IRL meet-up details]

NFT works as ticket to VVY YACHT event.

Included: Ticket to Yacht & 7 glasses of premium Champagne.

Date: Friday, August 26, 2022

Venue: Yeouido Marina Club & Yacht (160 Yeouido, Yeongdeungpo-gu, Seoul) /

Enjoy Networking & Party on luxury yacht, music play by special DJ

Dress Code : WHITE & GOLD

VVY NFT가 컬렉터블한 NFT 아트이자 & 요트 승선의 티켓입니다.
